description:
Final events are unfolding across the globe in rapid succession. We are fast approaching the closing scenes of world history and the final showdown for planet earth. Unprecedented events will soon rock this world to its very core. Join international speaker Dustin Pestlin for this life-changing adventure through the Bible. The greatest truths ever entrusted to mortal minds will be revealed in these free online meetings. Learn how to be ready for the final test – soon to be given to all mankind. You will identify the Antichrist, the Mark of the Beast, and be prepared for the most anticipated event in human history – the triumphant return of King Jesus. What's next in Bible Prophecy?

LEARN MORE (Free Registration) ➤ https://www.hopethroughprophecy.org/finaldays

November 6 - November 28th (presentations will be recorded and viewable afterwards)
